In installation, has written that cannot find file OWOW64WW in folder ENTERPRISE.WW, and it there is also any attempts have not helped to solve a problem, uploader/author, prompt the decision please.

sokolovds

You must replace OWOW64WW.cab with this one http://narod.ru/disk/12867998000/OWOW64WW.cab.html

Prichinu skachivanija pol'zovateljami nevernogo fajla CAB ja tak i ne ponjal. Predpolozhitel'no, ona taitsja v oshibke utorrent. Sam ofis pered vykladyvaniem proverjaetsja ne odin raz.
Vo izbezhanie dal'nejshego vozniknovenija problem pridetsja libo arhivirovat' (chto zapreweno pravilami mnogih trekerov), libo delat' obraz ISO s publikaciej kontrol'nyh summ.
